  "contents": [
    "c": "1",
    "style": "p",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "I am",
    "text": "I am",
    "text": " Zephaniah, the son of Cushi, the grandson of Gedaliah, and the great-grandson of Amariah, whose father was ",
    "add": "King",
    "text": "King",
    "text": " Hezekiah. Yahweh gave this message to me during the time when ",
    "add": "King",
    "text": "King",
    "text": " Amon\u2019s son Josiah was the King of Judah.",
    "style": "s1",
    "text": "The future destruction",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "2",
    "text": "Yahweh says,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\u201CI will \u25C4sweep away/destroy\u25BA everything [HYP] that is on the earth.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "3",
    "text": "I will sweep away people and animals.",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "I will sweep away birds and fish.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "I will get rid of wicked people;",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "there will be no more ",
    "add": "wicked",
    "text": "wicked",
    "text": " [HYP] people on the earth.\u201D",
    "style": "b",
    "style": "s1",
    "text": "Yahweh will punish Judah",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "4",
    "text": "\u201C",
    "add": "These are some of the things that I will do",
    "text": "These are some of the things that I will do",
    "text": ":",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "I will punish the people who live in Jerusalem and ",
    "add": "other places in",
    "text": "other places in",
    "text": " Judah.",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "I will destroy everything that has been used in the worship of Baal.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "I will cause ",
    "add": "people",
    "text": "people",
    "text": " to no longer remember the names of the pagan priests",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "or the ",
    "add": "other",
    "text": "other",
    "text": " priests ",
    "add": "who have turned away from me",
    "text": "who have turned away from me",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "5",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "I will get rid of",
    "text": "I will get rid of",
    "text": " those who go up on the roofs ",
    "add": "of their houses",
    "text": "of their houses",
    "text": " and worship the sun and moon and stars,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "those who claim that they worship me but ",
    "add": "also",
    "text": "also",
    "text": " worship ",
    "add": "their god",
    "text": "their god",
    "text": " Molech.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "6",
    "text": "I will get rid of all those who previously worshiped me but no longer do,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "those who no ",
    "add": "longer",
    "text": "longer",
    "text": " seek my ",
    "add": "help or ask me to tell them what they should do.\u201D",
    "text": "help or ask me to tell them what they should do.\u201D",
    "style": "b",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "7",
    "text": "Be silent in front of Yahweh the Lord,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "because it will soon be the time/day when Yahweh ",
    "add": "will judge and punish people",
    "text": "will judge and punish people",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "Yahweh has prepared to get rid of ",
    "add": "the people of Judah",
    "text": "the people of Judah",
    "text": ";",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "they will be like [MET] animals that are slaughtered for sacrifices,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and he has chosen ",
    "add": "their enemies",
    "text": "their enemies",
    "text": " to be the ones who will get rid of them.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "8",
    "text": "Yahweh says, \u201COn that day when I will get rid of ",
    "add": "the people of Judah",
    "text": "the people of Judah",
    "text": ",",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "I will punish",
    "text": "I will punish",
    "text": " their officials and the king\u2019s sons,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and ",
    "add": "I will punish",
    "text": "I will punish",
    "text": " all those who worship foreign gods [MTY].",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "9",
    "text": "I will punish those who ",
    "add": "show that they revere their god Dagan",
    "text": "show that they revere their god Dagan",
    "text": " by avoiding stepping on the threshold ",
    "add": "of his temple",
    "text": "of his temple",
    "text": ",",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and those who do violent things and tell lies in the temples of their gods.\u201D",
    "style": "b",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "10",
    "text": "Yahweh ",
    "add": "also",
    "text": "also",
    "text": " says,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\u201COn that day, people will cry ",
    "add": "out",
    "text": "out",
    "text": " at the Fish Gate ",
    "add": "of Jerusalem",
    "text": "of Jerusalem",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "People will wail in the newer part of the city,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and ",
    "add": "people will hear",
    "text": "people will hear",
    "text": " a loud crash ",
    "add": "of buildings collapsing",
    "text": "of buildings collapsing",
    "text": " in the hills.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "11",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "So, all you",
    "text": "So, all you",
    "text": " people who live in the market area ",
    "add": "of Jerusalem",
    "text": "of Jerusalem",
    "text": " should wail,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "because all those who sell goods and weigh out silver will be slaughtered.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "12",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "It will be as though",
    "text": "It will be as though",
    "text": " I will light lanterns to search in ",
    "add": "dark places in",
    "text": "dark places in",
    "text": " Jerusalem",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "for those who have become very satisfied with their behavior and complacent ",
    "add": "about their sins",
    "text": "about their sins",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "They think that ",
    "add": "I",
    "text": "I",
    "text": ", Yahweh, will do nothing to them,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "neither good things nor bad things.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "13",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "But I say that",
    "text": "But I say that",
    "text": " their valuable possessions will be plundered/stolen ",
    "add": "by their enemies",
    "text": "by their enemies",
    "text": ",",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and their houses will be destroyed.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "They will build ",
    "add": "new",
    "text": "new",
    "text": " homes,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "but they will not live in them;",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "they will plant vineyards,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "but they will never drink ",
    "add": "any",
    "text": "any",
    "text": " wine ",
    "add": "made from grapes that grow there",
    "text": "made from grapes that grow there",
    "text": ".\u201D",
    "style": "s1",
    "text": "The day of punishment",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "14",
    "text": "It will soon be the day/time when Yahweh ",
    "add": "will punish people",
    "text": "will punish people",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "It will be here quickly.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "It will be a time ",
    "add": "when people cry",
    "text": "when people cry",
    "text": " bitterly,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "a time when ",
    "add": "even",
    "text": "even",
    "text": " brave soldiers will cry loudly.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "15",
    "text": "It will be a time when ",
    "add": "God shows that he is",
    "text": "God shows that he is",
    "text": " very angry,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "a time when ",
    "add": "people experience much",
    "text": "people experience much",
    "text": " distress/suffering and trouble.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "It will be",
    "text": "It will be",
    "text": " a time ",
    "add": "when many things are",
    "text": "when many things are",
    "text": " ruined and destroyed [DOU].",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "It will be a time when it is very gloomy and dark [DOU],",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "when the clouds are very black.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "16",
    "text": "It will be a time when ",
    "add": "soldiers",
    "text": "soldiers",
    "text": " will blow trumpets ",
    "add": "to call other soldiers",
    "text": "to call other soldiers",
    "text": " to battle.",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "Your enemies",
    "text": "Your enemies",
    "text": " will tear down the walls around your cities",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and the high towers ",
    "add": "at the corners of those walls",
    "text": "at the corners of those walls",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "17",
    "text": "Because you sinned against Yahweh,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "he will cause you to experience great distress;",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "you will walk ",
    "add": "around groping",
    "text": "around groping",
    "text": " like [SIM] blind people do.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "Your blood will flow ",
    "add": "from your bodies",
    "text": "from your bodies",
    "text": " like [SIM] water,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and your corpses will lie on the ground and rot [SIM].",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "18",
    "text": "At the time that ",
    "add": "Yahweh shows that he",
    "text": "Yahweh shows that he",
    "text": " is very angry ",
    "add": "with you",
    "text": "with you",
    "text": ",",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "you will not be able to save yourselves",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "by ",
    "add": "giving",
    "text": "giving",
    "text": " silver or gold ",
    "add": "to your enemies",
    "text": "to your enemies",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "Because Yahweh \u25C4is very jealous/does not want people to worship any other god\u25BA,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "he will send a fire to burn up the entire world,",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "and he will suddenly get rid of all the ",
    "add": "wicked",
    "text": "wicked",
    "text": " people who live on the earth.",
    "c": "2",
    "style": "s1",
    "text": "A call to repentance",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "1",
    "text": "You people ",
    "add": "of Judah",
    "text": "of Judah",
    "text": " who ought to be ashamed,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "gather together [DOU].",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "2",
    "text": "Yahweh is extremely angry with you,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "so gather together now",
    "text": "so gather together now",
    "text": ",",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "before it is time for him to punish [MTY] you",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and blow you away like [SIM] ",
    "add": "the wind blows away",
    "text": "the wind blows away",
    "text": " chaff.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "3",
    "text": "All you people in Judah who are humble,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "worship Yahweh, and obey what he has commanded.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "Try to do what is right",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and to be humble.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "If you do that",
    "text": "If you do that",
    "text": ", perhaps Yahweh will protect/spare you",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "on the day when he punishes [MTY] people.",
    "style": "s1",
    "text": "Yahweh will punish Philistia",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "4",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "When Yahweh punishes Philistia",
    "text": "When Yahweh punishes Philistia",
    "text": ",",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "Gaza and Ashkelon ",
    "add": "cities",
    "text": "cities",
    "text": " will be deserted/abandoned.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "Ashdod ",
    "add": "city",
    "text": "city",
    "text": " will be attacked and the people expelled at noon ",
    "add": "when people are resting",
    "text": "when people are resting",
    "text": ";",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "the ",
    "add": "people of Ekron city",
    "text": "people of Ekron city",
    "text": " will ",
    "add": "also",
    "text": "also",
    "text": " be driven out.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "5",
    "text": "And terrible things will happen to you people of Philistia who live near the sea,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "because Yahweh has decided [MTY] that he will punish [MTY] you, ",
    "add": "also",
    "text": "also",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "He will get rid of all of you;",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "not one person will \u25C4survive/remain alive\u25BA.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "6",
    "text": "The land ",
    "add": "of Philistia",
    "text": "of Philistia",
    "text": " near the sea will become a pasture,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "a place for shepherds and their sheep pens.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "7",
    "text": "The people of Judah who \u25C4survive/are still alive\u25BA will possess that land.",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "At night they will sleep in the ",
    "add": "deserted",
    "text": "deserted",
    "text": " houses in Ashkelon.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "Yahweh will take care of them;",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "he will enable them to prosper again.",
    "style": "s1",
    "text": "Yahweh will punish Moab and Ammon",
    "style": "p",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "8",
    "text": "The Commander of the armies of angels, the God to whom ",
    "add": "we",
    "text": "we",
    "text": " Israeli people ",
    "add": "belong",
    "text": "belong",
    "text": ", says ",
    "add": "this",
    "text": "this",
    "text": ":",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\u201CI have heard the people of Moab and Ammon",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "when they insulted [DOU] my people,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and when they said that they would conquer my people\u2019s country.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "9",
    "text": "So now, ",
    "add": "as surely",
    "text": "as surely",
    "text": " as I live, ",
    "add": "I will destroy",
    "text": "I will destroy",
    "text": " Moab and Ammon",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "like [SIM] ",
    "add": "I destroyed",
    "text": "I destroyed",
    "text": " Gomorrah ",
    "add": "city",
    "text": "city",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "Their land will be a place were there are nettles and salt pits;",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "it will be ruined forever.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "My Israeli people who survive will take away all their valuable possessions",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and ",
    "add": "also",
    "text": "also",
    "text": " occupy their land.\u201D",
    "style": "b",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "10",
    "text": "The people of Moab and Ammon will get what they deserve for being proud,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "because they made fun of the people who belong to the Commander of the armies of angels.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "11",
    "text": "Yahweh will cause them to be terrified",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "when",
    "text": "when",
    "text": " he destroys all the gods of their countries.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "Then ",
    "add": "even the people who live on",
    "text": "even the people who live on",
    "text": " islands throughout the world will worship Yahweh,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "each in their own countries.",
    "style": "s1",
    "text": "Yahweh will punish Ethiopia",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "12",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "Yahweh says that",
    "text": "Yahweh says that",
    "text": " he will also slaughter the people of Ethiopia.",
    "style": "s1",
    "text": "Yahweh will punish Assyria",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "13",
    "text": "Yahweh will punish [IDM] and destroy Assyria,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "that land",
    "text": "that land",
    "text": " northeast of us.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "He will cause ",
    "add": "its capital",
    "text": "its capital",
    "text": " Nineveh to become ruined and deserted,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "a place that will be as dry as the desert.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "14",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "Flocks of sheep and",
    "text": "Flocks of sheep and",
    "text": " herds ",
    "add": "of cattle",
    "text": "of cattle",
    "text": " and many kinds of wild animals will lie down there.",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "Owls and crows will sit on the columns/pillars ",
    "add": "of the destroyed buildings",
    "text": "of the destroyed buildings",
    "text": ",",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "and they will \u25C4hoot/cry out\u25BA through the windows.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "There will be rubble in the doorways,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and the ",
    "add": "valuable",
    "text": "valuable",
    "text": " cedar boards will be taken ",
    "add": "from the ruined houses",
    "text": "from the ruined houses",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "15",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "The people of",
    "text": "The people of",
    "text": " Nineveh were ",
    "add": "previously",
    "text": "previously",
    "text": " happy and proud,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "thinking that they were very safe.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "They were ",
    "add": "always",
    "text": "always",
    "text": " saying,",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\u201COur city is the greatest city;",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "there is no city as great as ours!\u201D",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "But now it will become a ruins,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "a place where wild animals make their dens.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "And everyone who passes by there will hiss ",
    "add": "and scorn/ridicule that city",
    "text": "and scorn/ridicule that city",
    "text": ",",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and shake their fists ",
    "add": "to show that they detest that city very much",
    "text": "to show that they detest that city very much",
    "text": ".",
    "c": "3",
    "style": "s1",
    "text": "Yahweh will some day restore Jerusalem, whose people have rebelled against him",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "1",
    "text": "Terrible things will ",
    "add": "also",
    "text": "also",
    "text": " happen ",
    "add": "to Jerusalem",
    "text": "to Jerusalem",
    "text": ",",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "that city whose people have rebelled ",
    "add": "against Yahweh",
    "text": "against Yahweh",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "and who have become unacceptable to him ",
    "add": "because of the sins that they have committed",
    "text": "because of the sins that they have committed",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "They act violently toward others",
    "text": "They act violently toward others",
    "text": " and they \u25C4oppress/treat cruelly\u25BA ",
    "add": "other people",
    "text": "other people",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "The people there",
    "text": "The people there",
    "text": " do not pay attention to people who tell them ",
    "add": "the wrong things that they are doing",
    "text": "the wrong things that they are doing",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and ",
    "add": "try to",
    "text": "try to",
    "text": " \u25C4correct them/cause them to quit doing those things\u25BA.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "The people in Jerusalem",
    "text": "The people in Jerusalem",
